The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 52

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

The heat is on as The Block's last rooms, the first floor and roof top terraces, are up for judging. The winning team gets to pocket the $10,000 all for themselves plus they have a big decision to make that could help them win.
